== Charts ==
''Best Of...'' debuted at number 30 on the [[ARIA Charts|ARIA Albums Chart]] the week of April 15, 2012.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://themusic.com.au/news/all/2012/04/09/sia-dominates-international-charts/|title=Sia Soars at Home and Dominates US Club Chart|date=9 April 2012|accessdate=22 May 2012|work=themusic.com.au|publisher=Street Press Australia Pty. Ltd.}}</ref> The album reached a peak position of number 27 the following week before exiting the chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Sia&titel=Best+Of...&cat=a|title=Sia <U+2013> Best Of...|publisher=australian-charts.com|accessdate=22 May 2012}}</ref>

